於樓宇滲透不理想，亦非經常使用。以及今年政府將指配更多5G頻譜，包括3.3、3.5及4.9吉赫，包括5G黃金頻譜，公司將考慮參與這些頻譜拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n公司續指，由於市場上仍未有充足的流動裝置配合26及28吉赫頻帶，即使推出5G服務，亦暫未有全面的系統配合。公司將會密切留意市場發展，以衡量對該頻譜的需求。公司亦提到，由於26及28吉赫需設數以千計的無線電裝置，數目龐大，裝置亦具相當難度。"},{"pid":"0e07f18fcb45973831a76fb2cb1cad86372f3e83","tid":1032456,"uid":16061,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"+X哥: 無肉食 不了"},{"pid":"68409217ff5f7ca09eef4ec2d9c2805903d97231","tid":1032456,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"仲有佢個仔李澤楷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597157bdb7dfe3b91d4a60e9f3d40fa115c15e4d","tid":1032456,"uid":159448,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"標題黨黎講 你真係出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9cf13686bb572c62dae7a78f348c7d89055781","tid":1032456,"uid":83518,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"597157bdb7dfe3b91d4a60e9f3d40fa115c15e4d","tid":1032456,"uid":159448,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"標題黨黎講 你真係出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bf5cb03354b9ec946ee5bf8a88f01f9753c5b8","tid":1032456,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e07f18fcb45973831a76fb2cb1cad86372f3e83","tid":1032456,"uid":16061,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"+X哥: 無肉食 不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"正解，設備成本太高"},{"pid":"1b5cd625b4f0345